<% content_for :title, "About Us | Zoomora Toys" %>
<% content_for :meta_description, "Zoomora Toys is a family adventure store built around one idea: the best childhoods happen outside." %>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-[15px] py-8">
  <%= render Ui::BreadcrumbComponent.new(items: [
    { label: "Home", url: root_path },
    { label: "About Us" }
  ]) %>
</div>

<%# ---- Intro ---- %>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-[15px] pb-12 lg:pb-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center">
  <div>
    <p class="text-[12px] uppercase font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] text-red-600">About Zoomora Toys</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-[32px] lg:text-[40px] font-display font-bold text-ink-950 leading-tight">Adventure Starts Here.</h1>
    <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4 text-body text-grey-600 leading-relaxed">
      <p>Zoomora Toys exists around one simple idea: the best childhoods happen outside. Not in front of a screen, not stuck indoors waiting out the heat — outside, moving, steering something with a motor or pedals of its own.</p>
      <p>We started as a small team of parents tired of choosing between products that looked exciting online and arrived feeling flimsy in the driveway. So we built a store around a narrower promise: every ride-on, scooter, bike, golf cart, and ATV we carry has to hold up to the way families actually use it — every weekend, in real heat, for years.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-grey-50">
    <%= image_tag "hero-bicycle.jpg", alt: "", class: "w-full h-[280px] lg:h-[380px] object-cover" %>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- Story band ---- %>
<section class="bg-grey-50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-[15px] py-14 lg:py-16 flex flex-col gap-4 text-body text-grey-600 leading-relaxed">
    <h2 class="text-h2 font-display text-ink-950">Built On A Promise</h2>
    <p>That promise shapes everything else. We keep the catalog broad — from a toddler's first 6V ride-on to a full-size electric golf cart for the whole family — because adventure doesn't stop at one age group.</p>
    <p>And we keep the buying experience simple: clear pricing, honest descriptions, and a team that answers when you have a real question about a real product, not a script. We're based in Dubai and shipping across the UAE, with a catalog that keeps growing as we find products worth standing behind.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%# ---- What we care about ---- %>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-[15px] py-14 lg:py-16">
  <%= render Marketing::CenteredHeadingComponent.new(title: "What We Care About") %>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
    <%= render Marketing::TrustBadgeComponent.new(icon: "quality", title: "Built to Last", description: "We choose products for durability first, features second.") %>
    <%= render Marketing::TrustBadgeComponent.new(icon: "support", title: "Real Support", description: "Questions get answered by people who know the products.") %>
    <%= render Marketing::TrustBadgeComponent.new(icon: "warranty", title: "Stand Behind It", description: "Every vehicle we sell is backed by a manufacturer warranty.") %>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-[15px] pb-14 lg:pb-16">
  <%= render Marketing::CtaBannerComponent.new(
    title: "See What's New At Zoomora Toys",
    description: "Browse the full catalog and find the perfect ride for your family.",
    cta_label: "Shop All Products",
    cta_url: products_path,
    tone: :dark
  ) %>
</div>
